query:
UPDATE trips
SET
    landing_coverage = TSTZRANGE (LOWER(landing_coverage), $1)
WHERE
    trip_id = (
        SELECT
            trip_id
        FROM
            trips
        WHERE
            fiskeridir_vessel_id = $2
            AND period < $3
        ORDER BY
            period DESC
        LIMIT
            1
    )
RETURNING
    LOWER(period) AS ts
